# The `DbgValueHistoryMap` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

## Description {#details}

For each user variable, keep a list of instruction ranges where this variable is accessible.

The variables are listed in order of appearance.

Definition at line 46 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/dbgentityhistorycalculator-h">DbgEntityHistoryCalculator.h</a>.
